"{\"uid\": \"wallstreet-online.de-nachricht-17741540-petrolympic-welcomes-the-quebec-superior-court-s-decision-to-suspend-provisions-of-bill-21\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"TORONTO, Jan. 29, 2024 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- Petrolympic Ltd. (TSX.V: PCQ) (OTC: PCQRF) (the \\\"Company\\\") is pleased to report on the decision made by the Qu\\u00e9bec Superior Court (Civil Division) to stay some provisions of Bill 21, theAct ending exploration for petroleum and underground reservoirs and production of petroleum and brine(the \\\"Act\\\"), for the duration of the judicial proceedings.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 392, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 0, \"end\": 7, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Toronto\", \"score\": 0.9999724841127235, \"rank\": 2.747572386850273e-05, \"text\": \"TORONTO\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Toronto\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Toronto\"}, {\"begin\": 24, \"end\": 29, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/GLOBE\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"GLOBE\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/GLOBE\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/GLOBE\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Jan.\", \"from\": 9, \"to\": 13}, {\"ngram\": \"Petrolympic Ltd.\", \"from\": 43, \"to\": 59}, {\"ngram\": \"TSX.V\", \"from\": 61, \"to\": 66}, {\"ngram\": \"PCQ\", \"from\": 68, \"to\": 71}, {\"ngram\": \"OTC\", \"from\": 74, \"to\": 77}, {\"ngram\": \"PCQRF\", \"from\": 79, \"to\": 84}, {\"ngram\": \"(the \\\"Company\", \"from\": 86, \"to\": 99}, {\"ngram\": \"the decision\", \"from\": 126, \"to\": 138}, {\"ngram\": \"the Qu\\u00e9bec Superior Court\", \"from\": 147, \"to\": 172}, {\"ngram\": \"Civil Division\", \"from\": 174, \"to\": 188}, {\"ngram\": \"some provisions\", \"from\": 198, \"to\": 213}, {\"ngram\": \"Bill\", \"from\": 217, \"to\": 221}, {\"ngram\": \"exploration\", \"from\": 240, \"to\": 251}, {\"ngram\": \"petroleum\", \"from\": 256, \"to\": 265}, {\"ngram\": \"underground reservoirs\", \"from\": 270, \"to\": 292}, {\"ngram\": \"production\", \"from\": 297, \"to\": 307}, {\"ngram\": \"petroleum\", \"from\": 311, \"to\": 320}, {\"ngram\": \"brine(the \\\"Act\", \"from\": 325, \"to\": 339}, {\"ngram\": \"the duration\", \"from\": 347, \"to\": 359}, {\"ngram\": \"the judicial proceedings\", \"from\": 363, \"to\": 387}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In its ruling, the Court concluded to the legitimacy of Petrolympic's claim that some provisions of the Act represent a serious legal matter which, if not stayed immediately, would cause serious or irreparable harm to the Company.\", \"from\": 394, \"to\": 626, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"its ruling\", \"from\": 397, \"to\": 407}, {\"ngram\": \"the Court\", \"from\": 409, \"to\": 418}, {\"ngram\": \"the legitimacy\", \"from\": 432, \"to\": 446}, {\"ngram\": \"Petrolympic's claim\", \"from\": 450, \"to\": 469}, {\"ngram\": \"some provisions\", \"from\": 475, \"to\": 490}, {\"ngram\": \"the Act\", \"from\": 494, \"to\": 501}, {\"ngram\": \"a serious legal matter\", \"from\": 512, \"to\": 534}, {\"ngram\": \"serious or irreparable harm\", \"from\": 581, \"to\": 608}, {\"ngram\": \"the Company\", \"from\": 612, \"to\": 623}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Court also ordered provisional execution despite appeal of this ruling, meaning that the judgement will be enforced even if the Attorney General files an appeal.\", \"from\": 628, \"to\": 793, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Court\", \"from\": 628, \"to\": 637}, {\"ngram\": \"provisional execution\", \"from\": 651, \"to\": 672}, {\"ngram\": \"appeal\", \"from\": 681, \"to\": 687}, {\"ngram\": \"this ruling\", \"from\": 691, \"to\": 702}, {\"ngram\": \"the judgement\", \"from\": 717, \"to\": 730}, {\"ngram\": \"the Attorney General\", \"from\": 756, \"to\": 776}, {\"ngram\": \"an appeal\", \"from\": 783, \"to\": 792}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This exceptional measure aims at preserving the Company's rights while it continues to work toward a fair solution to the situation.\", \"from\": 794, \"to\": 928, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"This exceptional measure\", \"from\": 794, \"to\": 818}, {\"ngram\": \"the Company's rights\", \"from\": 838, \"to\": 858}, {\"ngram\": \"a fair solution\", \"from\": 893, \"to\": 908}, {\"ngram\": \"the situation\", \"from\": 912, \"to\": 925}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Mendel Ekstein, President, and Chief Executive Officer of Petrolympic, commented: \\\"We welcome this ruling as a crystal-clear message that the law must be fair.\", \"from\": 930, \"to\": 1089, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 930, \"end\": 936, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gregor_Mendel\", \"score\": 0.9999999999752163, \"rank\": 1.8532755631363533e-11, \"text\": \"Mendel\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gregor_Mendel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gregor_Mendel\"}, {\"begin\": 937, \"end\": 944, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hendrick_Ekstein\", \"score\": 0.9999999997776285, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ekstein\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hendrick_Ekstein\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hendrick_Ekstein\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"President\", \"from\": 946, \"to\": 955}, {\"ngram\": \"Chief Executive Officer\", \"from\": 961, \"to\": 984}, {\"ngram\": \"Petrolympic\", \"from\": 988, \"to\": 999}, {\"ngram\": \"this ruling\", \"from\": 1024, \"to\": 1035}, {\"ngram\": \"a crystal-clear message\", \"from\": 1039, \"to\": 1062}, {\"ngram\": \"the law\", \"from\": 1068, \"to\": 1075}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Petrolympic is not fighting Qu\\u00e9bec here, it is merely standing for its rights against an Act that we consider unfair and that unnecessarily harms the Company's interests.\", \"from\": 1090, \"to\": 1262, \"en